<h2>Important Warnings</h2>

<div class="notice-box">
<strong>Do Not Harass the Defendant:</strong> You must not harass, threaten, or take the law into your own hands. Always use official court enforcement procedures. Harassment can result in criminal charges and may undermine your legal position.
</div>

<div class="notice-box">
<strong>Insolvency Risk:</strong> If the defendant declares bankruptcy or enters into an Individual Voluntary Arrangement (IVA), enforcement action will be stayed (stopped). You will become an unsecured creditor in their insolvency proceedings and may only receive a small portion of the debt owed.
</div>

